{"tid":1295473,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉貼] 改善新移民帶來嘅問題 (求推)","createTime":"2019-07-08T04:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T12:40:43.000Z","uid":61161,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3f679f178581986e73c632c3452449c8c8233140","tid":1295473,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:39:48.000Z","msg":"社會搞到咁撕裂，政府、政界係咪應該做返啲野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2295401043832949&amp;id=907020282671039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2295401043832949%26id%3D907020282671039&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=97b24562\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2295401043832949&amp;id=907020282671039</a><br />\n<br />\n內文：<br />\n坊間有說法指，既然根據《基本法》第22條，單程證的審批權由中國負責，每日 150 個配額亦係中國決定，香港人點反對，香港政府都冇嘢可以做㗎啦！<br />\n<br />\n的而且確，單程證的審批涉及層層利益，中國高官會以每張150萬至200萬港元販賣單程證，亦是半公開的事情[1]，要打破牠們的利益，一點也不容易。<br />\n<br />\n但即使如此，港府亦非無事可做。《基本法》第154條同時保障了香港可實行出入境管制，所以喺我哋爭取到完全截停單程證之前，短期內港府絕對有權修改入境條例，對持單程證入境人仕施加合理及相稱的管制。<br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉，以下是我們認為一些可行且合理的建議：<br />\n<br />\n政府可要求持單程證人仕入境時需持以下證件：<br />\n<br />\n1）中港兩地所發的良民證<br />\n曾犯嚴重罪行、例如殺人[2]、的人仕，理應拒絕入境。這點理應沒有人會反對吧！<br />\n<br />\n2）驗身報告<br />\n如患有傳染病、例如肺癆、應在治好後才到港[3]。根據衞生署資料顯示，每年約有一百名內地肺癆患者移居香港，成為公共衛生的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n3）入息證明<br />\n申請人的在港配偶/親屬應有基本經濟條件支援申請人的生活。我們建議可參考美國，訂為貧窮線的 1.25 倍[4]。按最新數據，二人家庭的貧窮線是 $9800，即申請人的在港配偶/親屬應有$9800 x 1.25 = $12250 的收入，這是很基本和很合理的要求。<br />\n<br />\n當然，這些只是港府可獨自執行的短期措施而非終極目標。長遠而言，我們仍然建議港府需與中國政府商討調整單程證的名額，及實施措施吸引家庭到大灣區團聚。<br />\n<br />\n[1]販賣港單程證一張200萬　「河北王」落馬 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20160418/19576103\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160418%2F19576103&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=e09778cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160418%2F19576103&h=2274a99b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20160418/19576103</a><br />\n<br />\n[2] 入境大樓火劫 主角施君龍獲居權<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130824/00176_072.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20130824%2F00176_072.html&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=feece2c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130824/00176_072.html</a><br />\n<br />\n[3] 醫健：超級抗藥肺癆威脅港人<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20100321/00176_061.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20100321%2F00176_061.html&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=57d1077d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20100321/00176_061.html</a><br />\n<br />\n[4]  2019 Marriage Visa Income Requirements <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.boundless.com/immigration-resources/income-requirements-for-a-marriagebased-green-card/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boundless.com%2Fimmigration-resources%2Fincome-requirements-for-a-marriagebased-green-card%2F&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=4a1291c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.boundless.com/immigration-resources/income-requirements-for-a-marriagebased-green-card/</a>"},{"pid":"763d5e377acb3e175d50916b18c5aa34055d4944","tid":1295473,"uid":268327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EgD17zw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEgD17zw.png&h=0d0fa98c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295142\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295142</a><br />\n<br />\n集氣推推